without pruning,

00:18:23.680 --> 00:18:25.240
and a person won't succeed
without teaching.

00:18:25.240 --> 00:18:25.640
Right.

00:18:30.920 --> 00:18:33.880
Alright.
Let's resort to the punishing rod.

00:18:34.220 --> 00:18:34.980
Xilou.

